            "value": [
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/42215",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "This is a design decision that is clearly spelled out on the \"Zend_View_Abstract\" page (http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/manual\/en\/zend.view.abstract.html).\r\n\r\nZend Framework 2.0 will rectify this situation, but do not expect any changes before then.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-09-08T17:04:02.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-09-08T17:04:02.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/42216",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=dldinternet",
                        "name": "dldinternet",
                        "displayName": "Christo DeLange",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Thank you for taking the time to respond  but I disagree. \r\nI understand the whole rationale explained on the link you provided BUT it is perfectly possible to maintain the goals and protections set out in the manual AND allow derived classes to extend the base. This is a key OO concept ... \r\nNonetheless ... For now I will just duplicate the class hierarchy then ... ",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=dldinternet",
                        "name": "dldinternet",
                        "displayName": "Christo DeLange",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-09-08T18:35:33.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-09-08T18:35:33.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/42218",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I understand that you disagree. I also pointed out that we plan to rectify the situation for ZF2. We simply cannot at this time due as it would introduce BC breaks.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
